<project xml:id="cool-comoRestoAndre" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample response: First, Andre wrote 739 and 255 in expanded form and stacked them. Then, he subtracted 5 from 9 and got 4. Then, he realized he didn’t have enough tens to subtract 50 from 30 so he decomposed a 100 from the 700 into 10 tens to get 130. 130 minus 50 is 80 and 600 minus 200 is 400. His answer is 484.</p>
  </solution>


